{"abstract":[{"text":"Radio button item is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Radio button item covers a wider range of contexts by allowing to toggle the visibility of additional text labels and icon assets.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Layouts","level":2,"anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The radio indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Particular cases","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and optional texts and a custom radio trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Forbidden by design","level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, extraLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $selection, extraLabel: \"The Beatles\", description: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, a description, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  description: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  isError: true,","                  errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $selection)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $selection, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $selection, isReadOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}]},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(\"Cocorico !\",","                  isOn: $selection,","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading"},{"text":"Orange","level":3,"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Compact","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Compact","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Version","type":"aside"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem"]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(_:isOn:extraLabel:description:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(isOn:label:extraLabel:description:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"metadata":{"platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0"},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"ma